text:
Gulf Air Receives Southeast Asian Cargo Agents
Gulf Air, the national carrier of the Kingdom of Bahrain, recently received representatives from a number of Southeast Asian Cargo Agents, in the airline’s headquarters in Bahrain.
From the Philippines, representatives from all of Speedmark Philippines Incorporated, DSV Air & Sea Inc. and DHL Global Forwarding visited while, from Thailand representatives from Harpers Freight International Air Cargo Co Ltd., East-West Logistics Co., Ltd. and Trans Air Cargo Co. Ltd. all took part in what was an incentive and familiarization visit to Bahrain to experience the Kingdom and learn about Gulf Air’s product and service offering.
Gulf Air operates direct daily flights between both Bahrain and Manilla and between Bahrain and Bangkok.
